headline: Host Hotels & Resorts: Demand Signals Improve, But Macro Caution Remains
summary: Host Hotels beats Q3 expectations, raises guidance, and gains Moody's Baa2 upgrade, showing strong balance sheet trends. Check out why HST stock is a hold.
